The paper discusses the development of a scene-aware dialog system that integrates technologies from multiple research areas including end-to-end dialog systems, visual dialog, and video description. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
